Microphone mixer, a special effects recording software, in the recording can add a variety of music effects (applause, screaming, color, drums, etc.), podcast recording must app.

The following features are available:
1, (background) recording;
2, microphone tone adjustment;
3, around the channel, stereo channel;
4, scene simulation;
5, music effects (applause, cheering, screaming, etc.);
6, echo function;
